00:19:06,530 --> 00:19:08,000
I'll make a fortune.

289
00:19:10,600 --> 00:19:11,600
Don't worry,

290
00:19:11,600 --> 00:19:13,570
you'll still get your red envelope.

291
00:19:13,570 --> 00:19:14,600
It's only 200 every year.

292
00:19:14,600 --> 00:19:16,000
You think I care?

293
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:16,730
Fine, don't take it then.

294
00:19:16,730 --> 00:19:17,930
I'll save some money.

295
00:19:22,030 --> 00:19:22,970
Jiang Zhihao,

296
00:19:23,500 --> 00:19:25,500
you're not going to be like five years ago,

297
00:19:25,500 --> 00:19:27,200
being a useless freeloader,

298
00:19:27,200 --> 00:19:28,270
a zombie, are you?

299
00:19:29,430 --> 00:19:31,270
I'm begging you, don't do this to me.

300
00:19:31,270 --> 00:19:31,930
If Mom and Dad find out,

301
00:19:31,930 --> 00:19:32,600
Mom will go crazy.

302
00:19:32,600 --> 00:19:33,930
She'll ask me every day,

303
00:19:33,930 --> 00:19:35,100
'What should we do about Zhihao?'

304
00:19:35,100 --> 00:19:36,500
'Can you help figure something out?'

305
00:19:36,500 --> 00:19:37,400
And Dad will say,

306
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:39,530
'Zhihao can't go on like this.'

307
00:19:39,530 --> 00:19:40,570
Those two will drive me crazy.

308
00:19:40,570 --> 00:19:41,600
I'm already exhausted every day.

309
00:19:41,600 --> 00:19:42,370
I work at a hotel

310
00:19:42,370 --> 00:19:43,270
and help you with your job too.

311
00:19:43,270 --> 00:19:44,230
Stop nagging.

312
00:19:44,230 --> 00:19:46,160
I've put up with you for a long time.

313
00:19:46,670 --> 00:19:48,200
A talented young man like me

314
00:19:48,200 --> 00:19:50,370
needs to move up in society, I'm telling you.

315
00:19:50,370 --> 00:19:51,330
What exactly do you want?

316
00:19:51,330 --> 00:19:52,530
Just tell me.

317
00:19:52,530 --> 00:19:54,000
Jiang Zhilu,

318
00:19:54,000 --> 00:19:56,600
did you call me here just to watch you two fight?

319
00:19:57,930 --> 00:19:59,230
He's closing the breakfast shop.

320
00:19:59,230 --> 00:20:00,690
Help me get severance pay.

321
00:20:03,170 --> 00:20:04,270
I'll take 20 percent.

322
00:20:04,270 --> 00:20:05,330
Deal.

323
00:20:16,630 --> 00:20:18,130
Why are you closing?

324
00:20:20,030 --> 00:20:22,170
Of course I have my plans.

325
00:20:23,030 --> 00:20:24,330
What about you?

326
00:20:24,330 --> 00:20:26,330
Didn't you go to see Deng Yongkuan?

327
00:20:26,330 --> 00:20:27,500
What happened?

328
00:20:28,530 --> 00:20:31,000
He just wanted to solve it with money.

329
00:20:31,730 --> 00:20:33,300
He didn't even apologize once.

330
00:20:33,300 --> 00:20:34,870
That's too much.

331
00:20:37,470 --> 00:20:38,370
When I first found out

332
00:20:38,370 --> 00:20:40,130
that Deng Weikang was behind it all,

333
00:20:40,130 --> 00:20:43,300
I also thought about making a big deal out of it,

334
00:20:43,300 --> 00:20:44,930
blowing it up even more.

335
00:20:44,930 --> 00:20:46,900
But I quickly abandoned that idea.

336
00:20:47,470 --> 00:20:48,800
Do you know why?

337
00:20:51,930 --> 00:20:54,230
Because I thought when we meet again,

338
00:20:54,230 --> 00:20:56,560
it would definitely be very interesting.

339
00:21:00,100 --> 00:21:00,830
So,

340
00:21:00,830 --> 00:21:02,670
don't be so boring anymore.

341
00:21:02,670 --> 00:21:03,770
I'm boring?

342
00:21:03,770 --> 00:21:04,770
Yes.

343
00:21:05,270 --> 00:21:06,230
Let me tell you,

344
00:21:06,230 --> 00:21:07,800
the way rich people think

345
00:21:07,800 --> 00:21:09,900
is something ordinary people like us don't understand.

346
00:21:09,900 --> 00:21:11,430
If you want to fight against him,

347
00:21:11,430 --> 00:21:12,900
you need to be creative.

348
00:21:15,700 --> 00:21:16,900
Do you understand what unique means?

349
00:21:16,900 --> 00:21:18,370
You understand unique?

350
00:21:18,370 --> 00:21:20,770
I'm the definition of unique.

351
00:21:21,870 --> 00:21:24,100
Aren't you overestimating yourself?

352
00:21:28,670 --> 00:21:31,170
I won't let him get away with this so easily.

353
00:21:34,700 --> 00:21:36,370
Let me send you something.

354
00:21:37,430 --> 00:21:38,630
Check it.

355
00:21:40,900 --> 00:21:41,970
Did you get it?

356
00:21:45,430 --> 00:21:48,370
Girls do this when they like you.

357
00:21:48,370 --> 00:21:49,570
If you and this girl

358
00:21:49,570 --> 00:21:51,630
have your own little world,

359
00:21:51,630 --> 00:21:54,170
maybe a boring park or department store.

360
00:21:54,170 --> 00:21:55,730
Or the aquarium.

361
00:21:55,730 --> 00:21:58,330
Then she probably likes you.

362
00:21:58,330 --> 00:21:59,100
Hello everyone.

363
00:21:59,100 --> 00:22:01,500
I'm your dating coach... Oops, wrong file.

364
00:22:02,200 --> 00:22:03,600
That was what Niu Yifei was watching.

365
00:22:03,600 --> 00:22:04,570
Not mine.

366
00:22:04,570 --> 00:22:06,230
I'll send you another one.

367
00:22:07,300 --> 00:22:08,370
I've sent it to you again.

368
00:22:08,370 --> 00:22:09,930
Take a look.

369
00:22:09,930 --> 00:22:11,930
Remember, be unique.

370
00:22:22,230 --> 00:22:24,870
It was my mistake when I helped Deng Weikang

371
00:22:24,870 --> 00:22:27,870
and Linlin's breakfast shop.

372
00:22:27,870 --> 00:22:29,600
Because of my ignorance,

373
00:22:29,600 --> 00:22:31,870
I caused a toy factory to go bankrupt.

374
00:22:32,730 --> 00:22:35,700
I know time cannot be reversed.

375
00:22:35,700 --> 00:22:37,930
But I still hope to bring justice

376
00:22:37,930 --> 00:22:39,970
to those who were hurt.

377
00:22:50,400 --> 00:22:51,730
Dad's not home.

378
00:22:52,170 --> 00:22:54,730
He said a friend recommended a job to him,

379
00:22:54,730 --> 00:22:56,670
so he went to meet the boss.

380
00:22:56,670 --> 00:22:59,570
He might start working tonight.

381
00:22:59,570 --> 00:23:02,130
What job is so urgent?

382
00:23:02,130 --> 00:23:03,700
He's getting old.

383
00:23:03,700 --> 00:23:07,570
I hope it's not some physically demanding job.

384
00:23:07,570 --> 00:23:10,130
I think it's something in logistics,

385
00:23:10,130 --> 00:23:11,370
produce or something,

386
00:23:11,370 --> 00:23:12,170
working the night shift.

387
00:23:12,170 --> 00:23:12,770
I don't really know.

388
00:23:12,770 --> 00:23:14,500
Anyway, he understands

389
00:23:14,500 --> 00:23:16,070
that he's getting older

390
00:23:16,070 --> 00:23:17,670
and finding a job is difficult,

391
00:23:17,670 --> 00:23:19,430
so he took it as soon as he could.

392
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:21,430
He just got back.

393
00:23:21,430 --> 00:23:23,630
He should rest for a week or two.

394
00:23:23,630 --> 00:23:25,270
Why such a hurry?

395
00:23:25,900 --> 00:23:27,730
What else can we do?

396
00:23:27,730 --> 00:23:30,070
Creditors are already at our door.

397
00:23:31,570 --> 00:23:33,200
In today's society,

398
00:23:33,200 --> 00:23:36,930
people who've made mistakes don't get a chance to rest.

399
00:23:43,500 --> 00:23:45,130
Excuse me.

400
00:23:45,130 --> 00:23:47,190
Excuse me, just checking something.

401
00:23:49,300 --> 00:23:50,770
I told you to hold it properly.

402
00:23:50,770 --> 00:23:51,930
Why are you leaning on it?

403
00:23:51,930 --> 00:23:53,170
Hold it properly. Don't be lazy. Okay.

404
00:23:53,170 --> 00:23:54,270
What the hell?

405
00:23:54,900 --> 00:23:55,930
Hold this.

406
00:23:55,930 --> 00:23:57,390
I'm going to the bathroom.

407
00:23:58,670 --> 00:23:59,370
Hold it properly.

408
00:23:59,370 --> 00:24:00,470
Okay.

409
00:24:06,170 --> 00:24:07,730
I'm sorry.

410
00:24:19,500 --> 00:24:21,330
Are you even sleeping at all?

411
00:24:22,130 --> 00:24:25,200
You still have to work the night shift at the produce logistics center

412
00:24:25,200 --> 00:24:27,130
and hand out flyers in the morning.

413
00:24:32,400 --> 00:24:34,070
I did sleep a little,

414
00:24:34,770 --> 00:24:36,630
but I have no choice.

415
00:24:36,630 --> 00:24:38,900
Do you think I want to be like this?

416
00:24:38,900 --> 00:24:41,160
Then don't work the night shift anymore.

417
00:24:46,270 --> 00:24:48,430
Is there anything else you'd like to do?

418
00:24:48,430 --> 00:24:50,290
I can help you look for something.

419
00:24:51,270 --> 00:24:52,400
I do.

420
00:24:53,200 --> 00:24:54,600
I still want to be a boss.

421
00:24:56,270 --> 00:24:58,170
Are you being serious?

422
00:24:58,170 --> 00:24:59,700
Look at your situation now.

423
00:25:01,300 --> 00:25:02,600
Although I occasionally

424
00:25:02,600 --> 00:25:04,300
cut corners at the company.

425
00:25:05,070 --> 00:25:06,130
Saving wherever possible.

426
00:25:06,130 --> 00:25:08,270
But when it came to employee benefits,

427
00:25:08,270 --> 00:25:09,770
holiday bonuses,

428
00:25:09,770 --> 00:25:10,600
year-end bonuses,

429
00:25:10,600 --> 00:25:11,670
maternity leave,

430
00:25:11,670 --> 00:25:13,800
and overtime pay, I provided them all.

431
00:25:14,070 --> 00:25:15,470
I never

432
00:25:15,470 --> 00:25:17,300
pulled rank as a boss

433
00:25:17,300 --> 00:25:19,230
to make employees buy me drinks.

434
00:25:19,970 --> 00:25:20,930
I...

435
00:25:22,100 --> 00:25:23,970
I may not be a good businessman,

436
00:25:23,970 --> 00:25:26,430
but I think I was a decent boss.

437
00:25:41,700 --> 00:25:42,970
Whether you can get the toy factory back,

438
00:25:42,970 --> 00:25:44,370
I don't know.

439
00:25:45,930 --> 00:25:46,930
But the money they owe you,

440
00:25:46,930 --> 00:25:48,590
I will definitely get it back.

441
00:25:50,670 --> 00:25:52,730
I'll make the Deng family apologize.

442
00:25:53,170 --> 00:25:56,000
Let everyone know you were a good boss.

443
00:25:58,930 --> 00:26:01,330
Just focus on being a good boss, that's all.

444
00:26:12,500 --> 00:26:13,200
By the way.

445
00:26:13,670 --> 00:26:16,170
Don't you have cleaning work this afternoon?

446
00:26:16,170 --> 00:26:17,170
You should go now.

447
00:26:21,730 --> 00:26:22,800
I'm leaving.

448
00:26:35,230 --> 00:26:37,130
Don't get scolded again.

449
00:26:38,300 --> 00:26:39,570
I know.

450
00:26:42,870 --> 00:26:45,230
Take care of yourself.

451
00:26:50,770 --> 00:26:51,700
Senior.

452
00:26:51,700 --> 00:26:52,430
Did you receive

453
00:26:52,430 --> 00:26:53,900
what I sent you?

454
00:26:53,900 --> 00:26:55,130
Yes, I did.

455
00:26:55,770 --> 00:26:58,230
But this really doesn't have any news value.

456
00:26:58,270 --> 00:27:00,170
Deng Weikang and that woman called what's her name...

457
00:27:00,170 --> 00:27:01,500
Li Peizhen.

458
00:27:01,500 --> 00:27:02,100
My supervisor says

459
00:27:02,100 --> 00:27:03,730
they're not newsworthy people.

460
00:27:03,730 --> 00:27:05,130
Nobody knows who they are.

461
00:27:05,130 --> 00:27:06,070
Besides, that toxic toy

462
00:27:06,070 --> 00:27:08,170
was never even on the market.

463
00:27:08,170 --> 00:27:09,430
If someone had been hospitalized because of it,

464
00:27:09,430 --> 00:27:10,930
then it might have some appeal.

465
00:27:10,930 --> 00:27:12,070
We might be more interested then.

466
00:27:12,070 --> 00:27:14,300
My dad's factory went bankrupt!

467
00:27:14,300 --> 00:27:15,170
He's been hiding

468
00:27:15,170 --> 00:27:16,470
for years because of this.

469
00:27:16,470 --> 00:27:17,500
What is it? Is...

470
00:27:17,500 --> 00:27:18,700
So if nobody died,

471
00:27:18,700 --> 00:27:20,930
there's no news value, is that it?

472
00:27:20,930 --> 00:27:22,930
Liying, I know what happened to your family,

473
00:27:22,930 --> 00:27:24,800
but I really have some things...

474
00:27:24,800 --> 00:27:26,030
How can you still be

475
00:27:26,030 --> 00:27:27,490
so calm when talking to me?

476
00:27:33,630 --> 00:27:34,470
Senior, I'm sorry.

477
00:27:34,470 --> 00:27:35,300
I didn't mean...

478
00:27:35,300 --> 00:27:36,700
I wasn't targeting you.

479
00:27:37,230 --> 00:27:39,300
I suggest you help yourself.

480
00:27:39,300 --> 00:27:40,200
There are some methods

481
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:42,670
that might be more useful than traditional media like us.

482
00:27:42,670 --> 00:27:44,070
If you're interested,

483
00:27:44,070 --> 00:27:45,470
I can tell you about them.

484
00:27:46,800 --> 00:27:48,600
How am I supposed to help myself?

485
00:27:55,100 --> 00:27:56,530
Weikang, come on!

486
00:27:56,530 --> 00:27:57,570
I'll do it!

487
00:27:57,570 --> 00:27:58,470
This is very hot.

488
00:27:58,470 --> 00:27:59,570
Dangerous, Sister Peng.

489
00:27:59,570 --> 00:28:00,570
It's okay, I'll handle this.

490
00:28:00,570 --> 00:28:01,930
What if you get burned?

491
00:28:02,600 --> 00:28:03,530
It's hot!

492
00:28:03,530 --> 00:28:04,600
Careful!

493
00:28:04,600 --> 00:28:06,930
This soup smells amazing.

494
00:28:09,100 --> 00:28:11,000
Sister Peng, I brought

495
00:28:11,000 --> 00:28:12,130
you a gift from Singapore.

496
00:28:12,130 --> 00:28:13,700
You've been wearing this apron for a long time.

497
00:28:13,700 --> 00:28:15,070
I bought you a new one.

498
00:28:15,070 --> 00:28:16,730
You didn't have to.

499
00:28:16,730 --> 00:28:18,270
You take care of this home and Dad.

500
00:28:18,270 --> 00:28:19,400
You work so hard.

501
00:28:19,400 --> 00:28:20,100
Don't worry about getting it dirty.

502
00:28:20,100 --> 00:28:21,070
Okay, thank you.

503
00:28:21,070 --> 00:28:21,700
I'll fold it for you.

504
00:28:21,700 --> 00:28:22,700
Dad.

505
00:28:22,700 --> 00:28:23,570
Dad.

506
00:28:24,200 --> 00:28:24,770
No way.

507
00:28:24,770 --> 00:28:26,270
What's going on with Deng Weiyu?

508
00:28:26,270 --> 00:28:27,930
Didn't we agree to have dinner?

509
00:28:27,930 --> 00:28:29,790
Have some sense of time, will you?

510
00:28:33,670 --> 00:28:34,270
Sorry.

511
00:28:34,270 --> 00:28:35,270
You're early!

512
00:28:35,870 --> 00:28:37,100
I was working overtime.

513
00:28:37,100 --> 00:28:38,370
Come, let's eat.

514
00:28:43,400 --> 00:28:46,470
Weiyu will be transferred to be the manager of the Richu store.

515
00:28:46,470 --> 00:28:47,500
The Richu store.

516
00:28:47,930 --> 00:28:50,370
That branch with only a two-star rating.

517
00:28:50,900 --> 00:28:51,670
That's the one.

518
00:28:51,670 --> 00:28:55,600
The image store that gives ex-convicts a second chance at employment.

519
00:28:56,370 --> 00:28:58,830
Dad, we previously let ex-convicts work at Richu

520
00:28:58,830 --> 00:29:00,900
just to improve our social image.

521
00:29:00,900 --> 00:29:02,200
I won't even mention those thugs

522
00:29:02,200 --> 00:29:03,830
and what they've done to the store.

523
00:29:03,830 --> 00:29:04,830
We've been doing this for years.

524
00:29:04,830 --> 00:29:06,670
Now the lease is expiring.

525
00:29:06,670 --> 00:29:08,500
After we close the store,

526
00:29:09,500 --> 00:29:11,630
how will we reassign those employees?

527
00:29:17,330 --> 00:29:18,400
Those who should leave will leave.

528
00:29:18,400 --> 00:29:20,200
Those who should stay will stay.

529
00:29:22,570 --> 00:29:24,400
About the follow-up with Lequan and Xiaonong,

530
00:29:24,400 --> 00:29:25,900
let Weikang know,

531
00:29:25,900 --> 00:29:27,130
he'll follow up on it.

532
00:29:28,400 --> 00:29:29,330
No rush.

533
00:29:29,830 --> 00:29:32,830
I've been keeping track of the company's progress while in Singapore.

534
00:29:32,830 --> 00:29:34,430
Thank you for your hard work.

535
00:29:46,830 --> 00:29:48,270
What are you working on?

536
00:29:51,630 --> 00:29:53,030
Just looking through some documents.

537
00:29:53,030 --> 00:29:54,630
Richu Store,

538
00:29:58,470 --> 00:30:00,270
need any help with it?

539
00:30:00,270 --> 00:30:01,670
I don't think so.

540
00:30:06,030 --> 00:30:08,230
I wanted to tell you that

541
00:30:08,230 --> 00:30:10,600
whether someone gets fired by me, transferred to another department,

542
00:30:10,600 --> 00:30:12,130
or leaves voluntarily,

543
00:30:12,130 --> 00:30:14,860
I always organize a farewell party for everyone.

544
00:30:15,270 --> 00:30:16,630
Do you know why?

545
00:30:17,430 --> 00:30:18,170
Because maybe

546
00:30:18,170 --> 00:30:20,770
they're just not suitable for their current position,

547
00:30:20,770 --> 00:30:23,770
but could shine somewhere else.

548
00:30:23,770 --> 00:30:26,070
The farewell party is just an early congratulation

549
00:30:26,070 --> 00:30:28,530
for them becoming more valuable elsewhere.

550
00:30:29,300 --> 00:30:31,200
Then I won't organize one for you.

551
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:33,230
