552
00:30:33,230 --> 00:30:35,370
so let's just call it a vacation.

553
00:30:35,370 --> 00:30:38,130
You'll come back to the company someday, right?

554
00:30:46,630 --> 00:30:47,870
By the way.

555
00:30:49,200 --> 00:30:50,670
Remember,

556
00:30:50,670 --> 00:30:52,730
it's important to follow the right person.

557
00:30:52,730 --> 00:30:54,270
You know?

558
00:31:22,870 --> 00:31:23,800
Hello.

559
00:31:24,630 --> 00:31:25,130
Hi,

560
00:31:25,130 --> 00:31:27,530
