563
00:31:31,770 --> 00:31:34,130
You think a two-star rating is too high, don't you?

564
00:31:34,130 --> 00:31:35,730
Why can't it be eaten?

565
00:31:35,730 --> 00:31:37,330
I'm the assistant manager. Don't I know better?

566
00:31:37,330 --> 00:31:39,170
Just pour the sauce on it and it'll taste good.

567
00:31:39,170 --> 00:31:40,070
You weren't at the grill just now,

568
00:31:40,070 --> 00:31:41,930
